ww.theverge.com/2023/12/23/24013357/2024-chevy-blazer-ev-stop-sale-software-problems" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/23/24013357/2024-chevy-blazer-ev-stop-sale-software-problems</id><author><name>理查德·劳勒</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-23T13:22:41-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-23T13:22:41-05:00</updated><title> Apple Watch 禁令：你需要知道的一切</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple Watch Series 9，Siri 已启动&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4Z6yIXvDgbQ26QSMyIiKcV_jd5A=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/72982704/236790_Apple_watch_9_Ultra_2_AKrales_0356.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Apple 禁止销售 Watch Series 9 和Ultra 2 因专利纠纷在美国上市 - 以下是所有最新消息。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24009254/apple-watch-itc-ban-patent -dispute&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24009254/apple-watch-itc-ban-patent-dispute" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24009254/apple-watch-itc-ban-patent-dispute</id><author><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name><name>乔恩·波特</name><name>艾玛·罗斯</name><name>雅各布·卡斯特雷纳克斯</name><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name><name>宋茜</name><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-23T12:31:36-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-23T12:31:36-05:00</updated><title> Bose 的 QuietComfort Ultra 耳塞仍处于迄今为止的最低价格</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Bose QuietComfort Ultra 耳塞的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/6cwyrFr_ri90h-fdeHjs0ypVzFU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72993729/DSCF3082_Enhanced_NR.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;凭借出色的 ANC 和动感丰富的声音，Bose 最新的耳塞成为真正的热门产品。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;VKw8xm&quot;>;周六快乐，亲爱的读者！这是促销方面极其安静的一周，我们在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://ho